# OpenTrivia API Streamlit Experimental Quiz App 🚀

![Quiz App](quiz_app_screenshot.png)

Welcome to the Streamlit Experimental Quiz App! 🎉 Test your knowledge with 10 fun trivia questions on general knowledge. Get ready to challenge yourself and have some quiz-tastic fun! 🧠💡

## How to Run the Quiz App 🏃‍♂️

1. Install the required dependencies by running the following command in your terminal:

   ```
   pip install streamlit requests
   ```

2. Clone this repository:

   ```
   git clone https://github.com/your_username/streamlit-experimental-quiz.git
   ```

3. Navigate to the project directory:

   ```
   cd streamlit-experimental-quiz
   ```

4. Run the Streamlit app:

   ```
   streamlit run quiz_app.py
   ```

5. The app will open in your default web browser. Start the quiz and enjoy! 🎉

## How the Quiz App Works 🤔

1. The app fetches 10 trivia questions from the Open Trivia API. Each question has multiple-choice answers.

2. You will be presented with one question at a time, and you can choose your answer from the options provided.

3. After selecting an answer, the app will provide instant feedback on whether your answer is correct or not. 🤞

4. Your score will be calculated based on the number of correct answers you provide.

5. At the end of the quiz, the app will display your final score. Aim for a perfect 10/10! 🏆

